Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸也回了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽又發了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H736A82&\fs29\frz17.35\pos(467.666,317.333)}沒有忘記東西吧
